  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Monitor MR Key Figure Calculations</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"abstract\" content=\"Message logs and calculation details for calculation of market risk key figures based on market risk key figure sets.\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Message logs and calculation details for calculation of market risk key figures based on market risk key figure sets.\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loiofad0223ec5764d3cadf5896352033910\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Monitor MR Key Figure Calculations</h1><div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Message logs and calculation details for calculation of market risk key figures based on market risk key figure sets. </p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can monitor message logs and calculation details for the runs of the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"c4b94dd03c1f4f2c949992c36141f342.html\" title=\"Calculate and store the basic values needed for the calculation of the market risk key figures based on market risk key figure sets.\">Calculate Market Risk Key Figures</a> report\n(transaction <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">RAEP1_KFSET</span>).</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"loiofad0223ec5764d3cadf5896352033910__section_y4y_k3n_wmb\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"loiofad0223ec5764d3cadf5896352033910__ol_y3w_m3n_wmb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Call the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Monitor MR Key Figure Calculations</span> (transaction\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">AFWO1_KFSET</span>) in the area menu of the <span class=\"ph pname\">Market Risk Analyzer</span> under\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tools</span> or call the app on the SAP Fiori launchpad.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Execute the report directly to get a list of all runs executed or select a specifc run by entering selection criteria, such as\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Risk Key Figure Set</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Status</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Evaluation Date</span>,\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Created By</span>, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Created On</span>.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><div class=\"p\">From the result list, mark a line item and switch to the following data:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loiofad0223ec5764d3cadf5896352033910__ul_mfp_5jn_wmb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Execution Parameters</p><p class=\"p\">Shows the parameters of the calculation run, such as <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Evaluation Currency</span>,\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Scenario</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Filter</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Value-at-Risk Type</span> and\nso on.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Calculation Bases</p><p class=\"p\">Shows the concrete values of interest rates, FX rates, ans so on relevant for the calculation run.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Simulation Scenarios</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Log</p><p class=\"p\">Shows all messages for the calculation run.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Log History</p></li>\n</ul></div><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p>The calculations are divided into calculation packages, such as <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Net Present Value</span> and\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Value at Risk</span>. </p></aside></li>\n</ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}